args:
O power universal of the Qilin,
be bound by my solemn decree.
Sky-burning flash! Lightning caller!
May your exertions be suppressed!
Whoa! The thunder cloud vanished!\nGuess that's it then, yeah?
Yes, and I appreciate your help fending\noff fiends while I performed my work.
Hey, that's what we're here for!
What manner of relic was it this time?\nI would be MOST delighted to witness\nit with my own eyes!
Very well—but ONLY with your eyes!\nAre we perfectly clear on this?
This relic... It is... It is so...\nI MUST DISASSEMBLE IT!
All right, that's it. I'm sealing it away.
Honestly, how many times\ndo we have to go over this?
Only sealers should be handling relics.\nAnd though you are my travel companions,\nthis prescript still applies to you.
Now, let us return to the Halidom.\nI hope you will join me on my next quest.
You bet! It's my dream in life to\nrepay my debt to you, after all!
And what of me, hmmmmMMMM?\nAm I to be left in some tedious limbo?
Hmph! In that case, it seems I have\nno other alternative...
...Wait, you wanna be MY apprentice?!\nBut you're Xuan Zang's apprentice!\nOr, uh...her something, at least.
I have had an epiphany: If I am to gaze\nupward from the bunions of a master,\nshe must be in every way my superior!
So it MUST be you, Master Jiang Ziya!\nFor you are the finest sealer in the world!
Well, I AM sort of a genius...
(Hee hee! How easy it is to control\nsomeone who falls for base flattery!)

(And while I have a feeling there will be
many failures because of that, one cannot
make an omelet without breaking the
pale, sticky yolks of a few eggs...)
All right, you talked me into it.\nI'll be your master!
My eyeballs quiver in anticipation!\nPlease teach me the secrets of the relics!
...Oh, and let's keep this relationship\na secret from Xuan Zang, hmmMMM?
Errrr...it is for her own sake.
After all, she might be hurt to learn I\ncame to study under your superior skill!
Heck YEAH, she'd be upset about that!\nI basically yoinked you right out\nfrom under her nose, after all.
All right, we'll keep this all on the DL.
I never imagined that my training to\ncontrol relics would be so...so SEVERE!
M-mercy, master! Pray have mercy on me!
Nope! Now shut your trap\nand keep concentrating.
Th-this is madness... If I slip,\nI will fall into a pit of lava!
Oh, it's fiiiine! The relic'll totally\nsave ya if you fall.
And yet, has it not been slowly chipping\naway at my footing because you are\nFAILING to control it?!
Huh. I noticed he'd been absent of late,\nbut never considered he might have\ntaken up as another's apprentice.
You wanna head over there\nand give him the business?
No. He is Jiang Ziya's apprentice now,\nwhich means we have no business\nof which to speak.
And though she seems irresponsible,\nshe has gone through intense training.\nShe will take no half measures, this one.
This is an excellent opportunity for him\nto be tempered and honed... Oh ho...
You say stuff with a straight face that other\nfolks freak out at. You know that, right?
Well, hang in there, Sha Wujing.\nWe're rooting for you.
Aaaaaaugh! I'm going to fall!\nFor real, this time!
N-no... I cannot! I cannot die here!
For if I pass this test, I can use all of the\nrelics however I WAAAAAAANT!
